@@ -0,0 +1,46 @@
+# Phase 2.14 — Winner-Aware Routing Apply Controller for Routing Incident RCA
+
+## Цель
+Использовать experiment winner decisions для безопасного обновления default routing policy нового `routing incident RCA` контура.
+
+## Потоки
+- input: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_experiment_winner_decisions`
+- results: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_apply_results`
+- audit: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_apply_audit`
+- state: `cfg:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing:default`
+
